{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one big room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big oven, like a baker's oven, where you bake bread-- this type of an oven-- clay ovens, they were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And near the ovens, there was a place that you could sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really part of the oven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a warm part of the oven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everybody tried to sleep on that oven, really, because that was the warmest part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think I slept in-- you know, in one of the rooms, on a piece of-- you know, some kind of a-- like a bed made out of wood or, you know, whatever-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think that they had that only child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, in another part, my mother gave me to-- to other peasants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working as a cowgirl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to take out the cows to-- you know, to the pasture and spend the whole day with the cows.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to take them out in the morning and then bring them back at night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were treating me nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At least I had butter, and I had milk, and I had foot to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed with them as well, right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that I used to sleepwalk at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And very often, I would find myself outside the house, just-- and then they would, I guess, hear whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would bring me back in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So during the day-- I mean, while I was on the pasture, there was their son, too, or somebody else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you know, we were playing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in the-- picking whatever there was to pick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was another part of that-- of that ordeal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister was mostly with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
